{"tid":2114312,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"朗誦比賽語言由普通話轉至粵語","createTime":"2020-07-18T17:22:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-18T17:46:18.000Z","uid":105567,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"59d642a8c5706410a0906b99515cbea8cbf13092","tid":2114312,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T17:22:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h3fx4u6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh3fx4u6.jpg&h=4b89205a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n.<br />\n北區中學校長會早前向北區區議會申請撥款，以舉辦「北區中學聯校普通話演講比賽」。<br />\n.<br />\n對於比賽語言採用普通話，委員就此提出質疑。委員認為粵語更能讓本土學生以母語發揮，亦能讓鼓勵跨境或新移民同學融入本土粵語文化，更加適合作為比賽語言。<br />\n.<br />\n我動議要求議員就該比賽語言表態，結果零票普通話，一票英文，一票客家話，其餘所有委員全投粵語。<br />\n.<br />\n委員會根據表決結果，向北區中學校長提出條件，要求將比賽語言由「普通話」改為「粵語」，意味著如果北區中學校長會堅持把比賽語言定為「普通話」，將不會獲得區議會批出任何撥款。<br />\n.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/chiangmanching/photos/a.103274661023835/299626891388610/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fchiangmanching%2Fphotos%2Fa.103274661023835%2F299626891388610%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=Se3jk6qONbDe%2BTgec%2FNeBzbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=126ee39b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/chiangmanching/photos/a.103274661023835/299626891388610/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"780e9e4514a54c26f639e3112816c25c90fb7cf8","tid":2114312,"uid":199893,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T17:23:58.000Z","msg":"好波呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"868a1035c4f3903115dfbdd84b723b5b0a12d6c0","tid":2114312,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T17:24:27.000Z","msg":"普通話應該要喺香港消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21f761ba69980670fbaaf43eca6f5f06d0403be9","tid":2114312,"uid":29188,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202